1
00:00:40,800 --> 00:00:46,920
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL <i>DEEP AFFECTION EYES</i>
BY ER DONG TU ZI ON JJWXC.NET

2
00:01:01,160 --> 00:01:03,040
I haven't felt this happy in ages.

3
00:01:03,840 --> 00:01:04,760
Yeah.

4
00:01:05,280 --> 00:01:06,560
What…

5
00:01:07,080 --> 00:01:08,160
are your plans after this?

6
00:01:10,360 --> 00:01:11,320
No plans.

7
00:01:11,840 --> 00:01:13,960
I find life pretty relaxed now.

8
00:01:14,040 --> 00:01:16,000
No more weird complications.

9
00:01:16,520 --> 00:01:18,400
As for the future,
I'll take it one step at a time.

10
00:01:21,040 --> 00:01:23,880
You're all set
to start a new life. You're…

11
00:01:24,760 --> 00:01:27,440
not interested in a new relationship?

12
00:01:28,040 --> 00:01:30,200
I'm getting older.
Can't muster the energy anymore.

13
00:01:30,280 --> 00:01:32,720
Honestly, I think

14
00:01:32,800 --> 00:01:34,920
men are putting up
all the limits for women. Tired of it.

15
00:01:35,000 --> 00:01:38,280
Right now, I'm truly enjoying
this free-spirited happiness.

16
00:01:39,000 --> 00:01:40,760
Look. Freedom with my time,

17
00:01:41,280 --> 00:01:42,680
freedom to choose,

18
00:01:42,760 --> 00:01:45,520
and most importantly,
freedom with my emotions.

19
00:01:45,600 --> 00:01:47,960
That's why I don't want
to go back to that kind of hardship.

20
00:01:50,000 --> 00:01:51,680
And just to be clear,
this isn't aimed at all men.

21
00:01:52,240 --> 00:01:54,280
Kai, you're genuinely a good person.

22
00:01:55,320 --> 00:01:58,960
And I'm truly, deeply grateful

23
00:01:59,040 --> 00:02:01,360
for how you've cared for
and helped me and Jiayu all this time.

24
00:02:32,680 --> 00:02:33,720
What are you doing?

25
00:02:35,280 --> 00:02:36,280
Well, seatbelt…

26
00:02:36,360 --> 00:02:38,040
Seatbelt. My seatbelt…

27
00:02:38,120 --> 00:02:39,920
- What's wrong with the seatbelt?
- It's… It's broken.

28
00:02:40,000 --> 00:02:41,280
- What's broken?
- Yours is broken.

29
00:02:42,120 --> 00:02:43,160
Where is it broken?

30
00:02:43,680 --> 00:02:44,640
It's working.

31
00:02:44,720 --> 00:02:45,600
It's suddenly working.

32
00:02:45,680 --> 00:02:46,880
- Get moving now!
- Okay.

33
00:02:49,480 --> 00:02:50,880
Bye. Drive safe.

34
00:02:58,080 --> 00:02:59,040
Fang Ya'en!

35
00:03:00,600 --> 00:03:01,760
Happy divorce!

36
00:03:05,840 --> 00:03:06,920
Just go already.

37
00:04:46,400 --> 00:04:48,920
Jinyu, you're here.

38
00:04:49,000 --> 00:04:51,320
Didn't we agree to discuss
the Hailan Port Phase III project?

39
00:04:51,400 --> 00:04:52,320
Why are you the only one here?

40
00:04:53,480 --> 00:04:55,160
Someone else will be here soon.

41
00:04:55,680 --> 00:04:57,880
But before we get down to business,

42
00:04:57,960 --> 00:04:59,800
I need to speak with you alone.

43
00:05:00,600 --> 00:05:01,440
What is it about?

44
00:05:03,520 --> 00:05:04,960
Jinyu,

45
00:05:05,040 --> 00:05:05,880
I like you.

46
00:05:07,360 --> 00:05:09,640
Back then, to be closer to you,

47
00:05:09,720 --> 00:05:12,200
I cheered for you
outside the track when you raced.

48
00:05:12,280 --> 00:05:14,200
When you played basketball until midnight,

49
00:05:14,280 --> 00:05:15,720
I stayed with you until midnight.

50
00:05:17,120 --> 00:05:19,760
All these years,
my feelings haven't changed at all.

51
00:05:21,600 --> 00:05:23,360
Don't you like me even a little?

52
00:05:24,800 --> 00:05:26,720
I came to discuss the project.

53
00:05:26,800 --> 00:05:28,680
If it's about anything else,
let's drop it.

54
00:05:29,360 --> 00:05:30,280
I refuse.

55
00:05:30,360 --> 00:05:31,520
Auntie sent me here

56
00:05:31,600 --> 00:05:32,720
for our arranged marriage.

57
00:05:33,400 --> 00:05:35,360
Jinyu, I know you love to play

58
00:05:35,440 --> 00:05:36,760
and want freedom.

59
00:05:36,840 --> 00:05:37,960
I've thought it through.

60
00:05:38,040 --> 00:05:38,920
After we marry,

61
00:05:39,000 --> 00:05:40,600
I'd never interfere with your freedom.

62
00:05:40,680 --> 00:05:42,520
I'll be the obedient,
understanding perfect wife.

63
00:05:42,600 --> 00:05:44,360
Just let us be together.

64
00:05:44,440 --> 00:05:46,560
The arranged marriage was
my mom's decision. Nothing to do with me.

65
00:05:46,640 --> 00:05:47,480
I have matters to attend to. Leaving now.

66
00:05:48,960 --> 00:05:49,920
- Not happening.
- Let go.

67
00:05:58,960 --> 00:06:00,160
Jinyu,

68
00:06:00,240 --> 00:06:03,400
this is President Ye Kang
from our project's cooperative bank.

69
00:06:04,680 --> 00:06:06,240
What a coincidence.

70
00:06:06,320 --> 00:06:09,280
President Ye Kang's daughter
also works at Hailan Port.

71
00:06:09,800 --> 00:06:11,440
Ye Meng, to be exact.

72
00:06:11,520 --> 00:06:13,600
Manager Ye actually
accompanied Mr. Li and me

73
00:06:13,680 --> 00:06:15,360
on a tour around Ningsui
just the other day.

74
00:06:16,280 --> 00:06:17,160
President Ye Kang,

75
00:06:17,920 --> 00:06:19,800
this is Mr. Li, Li Jinyu,

76
00:06:19,880 --> 00:06:21,840
the lead of our Hailan Port project.

77
00:06:23,640 --> 00:06:25,640
- Hello.
- Sorry.

78
00:06:26,680 --> 00:06:28,080
I need to use the restroom.

79
00:06:37,360 --> 00:06:38,840
Lin Yangyang,

80
00:06:38,920 --> 00:06:41,760
you're much smarter than I imagined.

81
00:06:43,480 --> 00:06:44,560
Jinyu,

82
00:06:45,080 --> 00:06:46,280
what are you talking about?

83
00:06:46,360 --> 00:06:48,360
But petty cleverness is useless.

84
00:06:50,520 --> 00:06:52,040
You should focus your energy

85
00:06:52,120 --> 00:06:53,680
on understanding the project better.

86
00:07:05,080 --> 00:07:06,720
You've searched everywhere possible?

87
00:07:06,800 --> 00:07:08,080
Everywhere.

88
00:07:08,960 --> 00:07:09,960
Any updates?

89
00:07:10,720 --> 00:07:11,600
You're here.

90
00:07:13,080 --> 00:07:14,400
Did you find any clues?

91
00:07:15,880 --> 00:07:17,960
This guy's counter-surveillance skills
are too strong.

92
00:07:18,040 --> 00:07:18,920
Not a single trace.

93
00:07:20,840 --> 00:07:21,680
Jinyu's here.

94
00:07:22,280 --> 00:07:23,680
You two keep searching.

95
00:07:23,760 --> 00:07:25,760
Call if anything comes up.

96
00:07:26,280 --> 00:07:27,400
- Okay.
- Got it.

97
00:07:38,440 --> 00:07:39,760
Why the long face again?

98
00:07:39,840 --> 00:07:42,120
Did you and Ye Meng have another fight?

99
00:07:42,200 --> 00:07:43,160
Can't you wish me well?

100
00:07:45,280 --> 00:07:46,880
Ye Meng's dad is back,

101
00:07:48,600 --> 00:07:50,120
and he caught me

102
00:07:50,200 --> 00:07:51,760
having dinner with Lin Yangyang today.

103
00:07:52,280 --> 00:07:53,600
The worst part is
I couldn't explain myself

104
00:07:53,680 --> 00:07:55,080
in front of Lin Yangyang.

105
00:07:55,680 --> 00:07:57,320
So, now he thinks

106
00:07:57,400 --> 00:07:58,480
I'm the scumbag

107
00:07:58,560 --> 00:08:01,440
who deceived his daughter.

108
00:08:03,400 --> 00:08:05,760
Uncle Ye's actually spot-on about people.

109
00:08:10,080 --> 00:08:11,600
Now,

110
00:08:11,680 --> 00:08:14,160
you're practically caught red-handed.

111
00:08:14,240 --> 00:08:16,480
You can't clear your name now.

112
00:08:19,000 --> 00:08:20,720
This is tough to handle.

113
00:08:31,800 --> 00:08:32,880
What's that supposed to mean?

114
00:08:33,600 --> 00:08:34,960
You came to me today

115
00:08:35,039 --> 00:08:37,679
because you want your strategist
to give you some ideas, right?

116
00:08:38,360 --> 00:08:39,640
Now that you're so wealthy,

117
00:08:40,559 --> 00:08:42,200
I can't keep providing free services.

118
00:08:42,280 --> 00:08:43,919
Why so confident?

119
00:08:44,000 --> 00:08:45,240
When have you ever helped
without making things worse?

120
00:08:45,840 --> 00:08:47,640
This time, think carefully.

121
00:08:47,720 --> 00:08:50,320
I've been running to Ye Meng's house
since childhood,

122
00:08:50,400 --> 00:08:52,040
saw Uncle Ye plenty.

123
00:08:52,120 --> 00:08:54,240
My combat experience is through the roof.

124
00:08:57,280 --> 00:08:59,720
If you can't handle it,
I'll go to Gou Kai.

125
00:08:59,800 --> 00:09:01,480
At least he pays me 250.

126
00:09:02,280 --> 00:09:03,560
Fine. I'll pay.

127
00:09:08,240 --> 00:09:09,080
Transfer done.

128
00:09:09,160 --> 00:09:10,920
8.88 YUAN, PLEASE CONFIRM RECEIPT

129
00:09:11,880 --> 00:09:14,160
Seriously, bro? You're still this stingy?

130
00:09:14,240 --> 00:09:15,800
You're loaded now but only

131
00:09:15,880 --> 00:09:17,280
gave 8.88?

132
00:09:17,360 --> 00:09:19,080
Take it or I'm canceling it.

133
00:09:19,160 --> 00:09:20,520
RECEIVING

134
00:09:22,720 --> 00:09:23,880
Got it.

135
00:09:25,240 --> 00:09:26,200
Let me show you how it's done.

136
00:09:26,280 --> 00:09:28,880
Uncle Ye works at a bank.

137
00:09:28,960 --> 00:09:31,080
Throwing money at him won't work.

138
00:09:31,600 --> 00:09:33,160
Tell me something I don't know.

139
00:09:33,240 --> 00:09:34,520
Enough setup. Just say it already.

140
00:09:36,200 --> 00:09:37,280
Uncle Ye

141
00:09:37,880 --> 00:09:40,200
has a soft spot for kids
who graduated from top-tier universities.

142
00:09:40,280 --> 00:09:41,840
He really values academic excellence.

143
00:09:42,520 --> 00:09:43,720
Your…

144
00:09:44,360 --> 00:09:45,720
high school background won't cut it.

145
00:09:45,800 --> 00:09:47,920
Go get yourself a diploma

146
00:09:48,000 --> 00:09:49,480
from one of the first-class universities.

147
00:09:51,720 --> 00:09:53,360
So, this is your brilliant idea?

148
00:09:53,880 --> 00:09:55,360
Seriously, bro, can you be
even the slightest bit useful?

149
00:09:55,440 --> 00:09:56,920
This is totally solid!

150
00:09:57,000 --> 00:09:58,760
If you can't manage it,
I'll take you there myself.

151
00:09:58,840 --> 00:10:00,960
Forget it. I've finally figured it out.

152
00:10:01,040 --> 00:10:03,760
Ye Meng's dad just doesn't like you.
It has nothing to do with your education.

153
00:10:04,360 --> 00:10:05,440
Look who's talking.

154
00:10:05,520 --> 00:10:07,400
Why don't you just ask Ye Meng directly?

155
00:10:07,480 --> 00:10:09,400
She definitely knows her dad best.

156
00:10:09,920 --> 00:10:12,480
Right now,
she's having dinner with her dad.

157
00:10:13,360 --> 00:10:15,960
I just hope
I can still get through the door

158
00:10:16,040 --> 00:10:17,240
when I go back tonight.

159
00:10:19,120 --> 00:10:22,120
Brothers from the inside.
Good luck. You're on your own.

160
00:10:23,240 --> 00:10:24,720
Wait, what do you mean by that?

161
00:10:24,800 --> 00:10:25,760
Give me my money back.

162
00:10:25,840 --> 00:10:27,600
Is there any
financial transaction between us?

163
00:10:27,680 --> 00:10:29,440
You're ridiculous.
Who do you think you are?

164
00:10:49,760 --> 00:10:51,080
Honey, you're back.

165
00:10:51,600 --> 00:10:53,400
I bought a bunch
of your favorite fruits today.

166
00:10:53,480 --> 00:10:54,440
Cut them up myself.

167
00:10:54,520 --> 00:10:55,680
Here, try some.

168
00:10:57,960 --> 00:10:59,360
You must be tired after the long day.

169
00:10:59,440 --> 00:11:00,520
Have some water.

170
00:11:04,760 --> 00:11:06,120
Thank you for being so thoughtful.

171
00:11:06,200 --> 00:11:07,760
I actually brought some fruit back too.
Here, try some.

172
00:11:10,520 --> 00:11:11,560
Here.

173
00:11:15,040 --> 00:11:16,080
Oh, durian?

174
00:11:19,840 --> 00:11:21,480
You don't even like durian.

175
00:11:21,560 --> 00:11:22,760
Why did you buy it?

176
00:11:22,840 --> 00:11:24,360
Your father-in-law
asked me to bring it back.

177
00:11:24,440 --> 00:11:25,720
Said our home could use one.

178
00:11:27,400 --> 00:11:29,560
Honey, this…

179
00:11:30,080 --> 00:11:31,320
We already have a washboard at home.

180
00:11:31,400 --> 00:11:33,440
Even a keyboard
would work if needed, right?

181
00:11:33,520 --> 00:11:34,600
This…

182
00:11:34,680 --> 00:11:35,800
really isn't necessary.

183
00:11:35,880 --> 00:11:37,320
A washboard doesn't leave
a lasting impression.

184
00:11:37,400 --> 00:11:38,680
This does.

185
00:11:43,040 --> 00:11:43,880
Did Dad tell you everything?

186
00:11:45,200 --> 00:11:47,240
He told me it was quite the scene.

187
00:11:47,320 --> 00:11:49,680
Not just a confession,
but also a high-society arranged marriage.

188
00:11:49,760 --> 00:11:51,120
My dad doesn't usually watch dramas,

189
00:11:51,200 --> 00:11:53,200
but he said
it was more entertaining than any show.

190
00:11:55,360 --> 00:11:57,760
A father-in-law judging his son-in-law

191
00:11:57,840 --> 00:12:00,280
was already like facing
a rival who "stole" his daughter.

192
00:12:00,800 --> 00:12:02,360
But this time, I'm completely done for.

193
00:12:03,240 --> 00:12:04,480
Honey.

194
00:12:05,440 --> 00:12:06,600
I was wrong.

195
00:12:07,120 --> 00:12:09,280
Do you think you could help me?

196
00:12:10,200 --> 00:12:12,160
Help me salvage my image

197
00:12:12,240 --> 00:12:13,600
in front of your dad?

198
00:12:14,160 --> 00:12:16,840
Otherwise, if he forces us to divorce,
I'd be so wronged.

199
00:12:20,800 --> 00:12:22,160
If it really comes to it,

200
00:12:22,240 --> 00:12:24,000
I'll deal with this durian.

201
00:12:30,640 --> 00:12:31,600
I…

202
00:12:34,960 --> 00:12:35,960
I'm putting it down.

203
00:12:36,760 --> 00:12:38,280
I'm going to plead guilty
and ask for punishment.

204
00:12:40,520 --> 00:12:41,480
Aren't you going to stop me?

205
00:12:41,560 --> 00:12:43,760
Why would I stop you?

206
00:12:43,840 --> 00:12:45,320
Where exactly does this thing even hurt?

207
00:12:45,400 --> 00:12:47,280
It'll hurt your hand. Is it bleeding?

208
00:12:53,680 --> 00:12:54,520
I was wrong.

209
00:12:54,600 --> 00:12:55,880
What exactly were you wrong about?

210
00:12:55,960 --> 00:12:57,040
I was wrong about everything.

211
00:13:00,120 --> 00:13:01,320
Please, help me out.

212
00:13:02,120 --> 00:13:03,240
Alright.

213
00:13:03,320 --> 00:13:05,760
If you really want to win over my dad,

214
00:13:05,840 --> 00:13:07,800
you need to start
with his hobbies and interests.

215
00:13:08,520 --> 00:13:09,760
Hobbies and interests?

216
00:13:23,880 --> 00:13:24,960
Dad.

217
00:14:01,960 --> 00:14:03,080
Dad,

218
00:14:03,160 --> 00:14:06,040
I heard from Ye Meng
that you really enjoy fishing.

219
00:14:06,120 --> 00:14:07,880
I specially prepared some bait for you.

220
00:14:09,280 --> 00:14:10,320
Would you like to give it a try?

221
00:14:12,280 --> 00:14:14,760
I'm sorry,
but our bank has strict policies.

222
00:14:14,840 --> 00:14:15,880
We can't accept gifts.

223
00:14:18,680 --> 00:14:20,080
We're family.

224
00:14:20,600 --> 00:14:22,320
This is just a son-in-law

225
00:14:22,400 --> 00:14:23,920
showing respect to his father-in-law.

226
00:14:57,280 --> 00:14:58,760
How did you set up the fishing spot?

227
00:15:00,600 --> 00:15:02,560
I use precision baiting,

228
00:15:02,640 --> 00:15:03,520
keeping the groundbait
and hookbait separate.

229
00:15:04,920 --> 00:15:05,800
Well,

230
00:15:05,880 --> 00:15:08,400
fish won't easily swim
to the center of the bait zone.

231
00:15:10,120 --> 00:15:13,800
I'm using black rice
mixed with bloodworms.

232
00:15:13,880 --> 00:15:14,920
Maybe you should give it a try too?

233
00:15:17,840 --> 00:15:19,600
Black rice and bloodworms?

234
00:15:20,480 --> 00:15:21,880
Give it a try? Alright.

235
00:15:24,040 --> 00:15:25,160
Let me give it a try.

236
00:15:36,040 --> 00:15:36,960
Dad.

237
00:15:39,400 --> 00:15:41,360
The Ms. Lin you saw yesterday

238
00:15:41,880 --> 00:15:44,400
was just someone Mom arranged for me
as a marriage of convenience.

239
00:15:45,080 --> 00:15:47,640
I never had any real connection with her.

240
00:15:47,720 --> 00:15:51,320
It's just that Ye Meng and I
are keeping our marriage private for now,

241
00:15:51,840 --> 00:15:53,600
so it wasn't the right time
to make it public.

242
00:15:55,200 --> 00:15:56,040
Hiding your marriage like this…

243
00:15:57,400 --> 00:15:59,080
What do you take our Ye Meng for?

244
00:15:59,960 --> 00:16:02,240
You've got the wrong idea. My feelings
for Ye Meng are completely genuine.

245
00:16:03,040 --> 00:16:05,600
It's just that
I've just joined the company,

246
00:16:06,120 --> 00:16:08,440
and if this gets out,

247
00:16:08,520 --> 00:16:10,200
it could start a lot of gossip.

248
00:16:10,280 --> 00:16:12,040
I'm afraid she would get hurt.

249
00:16:12,640 --> 00:16:14,040
Save your explanations.

250
00:16:14,880 --> 00:16:16,840
I've met plenty of rich kids like you.

251
00:16:28,040 --> 00:16:29,120
Looks like there's one.

252
00:16:30,120 --> 00:16:31,160
It might be a big one.

253
00:16:31,840 --> 00:16:33,160
One, two, three.

254
00:16:37,520 --> 00:16:39,080
- It's fine. Come on, Dad.
- Come here.

255
00:16:39,160 --> 00:16:40,720
Here's the rod. I'll get this.

256
00:16:47,920 --> 00:16:49,000
How is it?

257
00:16:50,440 --> 00:16:51,680
Over here, Dad.

258
00:16:51,760 --> 00:16:52,880
This one's a big catch.

259
00:16:54,880 --> 00:16:56,040
Didn't expect it to be this huge.

260
00:16:57,680 --> 00:16:59,080
Get up here, now.

261
00:16:59,160 --> 00:17:00,120
Come on.

262
00:17:05,000 --> 00:17:06,000
Meng.

263
00:17:06,640 --> 00:17:08,440
- Look at the fish your dad caught.
- You're finally back!

264
00:17:08,520 --> 00:17:10,119
It's already gotten dark.

265
00:17:11,800 --> 00:17:13,119
Take a look.

266
00:17:13,839 --> 00:17:15,680
How do you wanna cook this fish?

267
00:17:18,520 --> 00:17:19,359
Li Jinyu.

268
00:17:20,240 --> 00:17:21,359
What happened to your pants?

269
00:17:21,960 --> 00:17:23,680
