00:29:03,720 --> 00:29:06,280
<i>but still couldn't find</i>
<i>any trace of that person.</i>

537
00:29:07,200 --> 00:29:08,480
<i>Within days,</i>

538
00:29:08,560 --> 00:29:10,480
<i>the other investors</i>

539
00:29:10,560 --> 00:29:11,800
<i>started causing a scene</i>
<i>at the welfare center.</i>

540
00:29:13,120 --> 00:29:15,200
He cheated me out of all my money too!

541
00:29:20,160 --> 00:29:21,360
<i>There was nothing she could do.</i>

542
00:29:21,920 --> 00:29:22,920
<i>Your mom was desperate too.</i>

543
00:29:23,560 --> 00:29:25,280
<i>Without telling any of us,</i>

544
00:29:25,360 --> 00:29:26,880
<i>she went alone</i>

545
00:29:26,960 --> 00:29:29,400
<i>to Jiangbei to find that man.</i>

546
00:29:37,040 --> 00:29:38,920
Why was I kept in the dark about all this?

547
00:29:41,480 --> 00:29:42,960
I told them not to tell you.

548
00:29:45,840 --> 00:29:46,720
Dad.

549
00:29:54,600 --> 00:29:55,480
Meng.

550
00:29:58,040 --> 00:30:00,600
I didn't want you
to see your mom in a bad state

551
00:30:00,680 --> 00:30:01,720
before she passed,

552
00:30:03,400 --> 00:30:05,120
and I didn't want people
to gossip about her

553
00:30:05,200 --> 00:30:07,240
or stab her in the back
after she was gone.

554
00:30:07,320 --> 00:30:08,600
Besides,

555
00:30:08,680 --> 00:30:09,560
hasn't Wang Xingsheng

556
00:30:09,640 --> 00:30:11,840
already been arrested and sentenced?

557
00:30:11,920 --> 00:30:13,280
So, I believe this

558
00:30:13,360 --> 00:30:15,560
should end here.

559
00:30:18,440 --> 00:30:19,440
Dad.

560
00:30:21,480 --> 00:30:24,320
Do you have any idea
how I've lived all these years?

561
00:30:30,600 --> 00:30:33,960
Every day, I'm filled with guilt and pain

562
00:30:35,120 --> 00:30:38,640
because I believe Mom became depressed
because of my poor grades.

563
00:30:38,720 --> 00:30:41,480
Honestly, I don't know what to do either.

564
00:30:43,120 --> 00:30:44,280
I…

565
00:30:44,360 --> 00:30:46,920
I thought keeping you in the dark
was for your own good.

566
00:30:49,600 --> 00:30:50,560
Right.

567
00:30:52,560 --> 00:30:54,520
You all think it's for my own good.

568
00:30:57,240 --> 00:30:59,160
But have you ever
really considered how I feel?

569
00:31:01,840 --> 00:31:02,760
Meng.

570
00:31:03,280 --> 00:31:04,240
Meng!

571
00:31:04,320 --> 00:31:05,480
Don't worry.

572
00:31:06,040 --> 00:31:06,960
I'll go find her.

573
00:31:22,200 --> 00:31:25,400
CLOUDWILD WANDERING, FRIENDS LIST

574
00:31:30,760 --> 00:31:32,400
Why did you

575
00:31:32,480 --> 00:31:33,920
come here alone to play games?

576
00:31:34,440 --> 00:31:35,440
Get some fresh air.

577
00:31:36,200 --> 00:31:38,040
Put something on. Don't catch a cold.

578
00:31:43,560 --> 00:31:44,840
This game

579
00:31:44,920 --> 00:31:46,280
probably doesn't have
many players anymore, does it?

580
00:31:49,120 --> 00:31:50,440
Not many people play it anymore.

581
00:31:51,320 --> 00:31:53,160
I used to play this game
a lot with my mom.

582
00:31:54,120 --> 00:31:55,600
Whenever we teamed up,

583
00:31:56,360 --> 00:31:57,800
we had a 100% win rate.

584
00:32:00,040 --> 00:32:02,160
The ultimate duo. Pretty cool.

585
00:32:02,760 --> 00:32:05,040
We used to often play games

586
00:32:05,560 --> 00:32:07,680
<i>and gossip together</i>

587
00:32:07,760 --> 00:32:08,960
<i>on this terrace.</i>

588
00:32:09,840 --> 00:32:12,000
<i>My mom knew so many of my secrets,</i>

589
00:32:12,720 --> 00:32:15,640
<i>but she never lectured me as a mother.</i>

590
00:32:17,680 --> 00:32:19,560
She never placed any demands on me.

591
00:32:22,320 --> 00:32:23,600
She often said,

592
00:32:25,240 --> 00:32:26,240
"Meng,

593
00:32:27,320 --> 00:32:28,680
nothing else matters.

594
00:32:30,600 --> 00:32:32,240
Your happiness
is the most important thing."

595
00:32:36,080 --> 00:32:37,200
To you,

596
00:32:38,160 --> 00:32:39,440
she wasn't just a mother.

597
00:32:40,560 --> 00:32:42,080
She was your best friend.

598
00:32:47,680 --> 00:32:50,000
That's why you resent your dad

599
00:32:50,080 --> 00:32:52,120
for not telling you the truth.

600
00:32:55,440 --> 00:32:56,560
But I can tell

601
00:32:56,640 --> 00:32:58,600
that your dad also loves you deeply.

602
00:32:59,720 --> 00:33:01,040
Maybe

603
00:33:01,560 --> 00:33:03,320
he just wanted you to live a happy life,

604
00:33:03,400 --> 00:33:04,520
without carrying this burden.

605
00:33:07,360 --> 00:33:09,040
More like running away from it.

606
00:33:14,240 --> 00:33:15,320
How about

607
00:33:15,400 --> 00:33:17,840
we find a chance to have a meal together?

608
00:33:17,920 --> 00:33:20,080
You and Dad should sit down
and have a proper talk.

609
00:33:29,040 --> 00:33:30,320
I don't want to talk.

610
00:33:30,400 --> 00:33:31,480
There's nothing left to say.

611
00:33:35,240 --> 00:33:36,240
We're all family.

612
00:33:37,080 --> 00:33:39,440
In a family, grudges don't last overnight,

613
00:33:39,520 --> 00:33:40,480
right?

614
00:33:49,080 --> 00:33:50,320
Wait,

615
00:33:50,840 --> 00:33:52,080
that doesn't sound right.

616
00:33:52,160 --> 00:33:54,080
Why does it seem like
you've suddenly teamed up with my dad?

617
00:33:54,160 --> 00:33:55,840
How could that be?

618
00:33:56,360 --> 00:33:58,160
I'll always be on your side.

619
00:33:58,240 --> 00:33:59,240
My stance is clear.

620
00:33:59,840 --> 00:34:00,720
Look,

621
00:34:00,800 --> 00:34:03,000
if you're doing well,
Dad's doing well, then I'm doing well.

622
00:34:03,080 --> 00:34:04,040
But, of course,

623
00:34:04,120 --> 00:34:05,520
you're the one who matters most.

624
00:34:11,159 --> 00:34:12,199
Come on.

625
00:34:15,040 --> 00:34:16,440
No more crying,

626
00:34:17,600 --> 00:34:19,040
or your eyes will be puffy tomorrow.

627
00:34:23,560 --> 00:34:24,520
Thank you.

628
00:34:25,120 --> 00:34:26,440
What are you thanking me for?

629
00:34:28,840 --> 00:34:29,800
Okay?

630
00:34:31,840 --> 00:34:33,320
Alright.

631
00:34:35,719 --> 00:34:37,920
You won't look pretty tomorrow
with puffy eyes.

632
00:34:39,520 --> 00:34:40,719
Got it.

633
00:34:47,520 --> 00:34:48,440
Yangyang,

634
00:34:48,520 --> 00:34:50,120
how did it go with Jinyu?

635
00:34:51,800 --> 00:34:53,840
That's just how he is.

636
00:34:53,920 --> 00:34:55,960
Always a bit cold
and distant with everyone.

637
00:34:56,040 --> 00:34:57,760
Don't worry, I'll be in Ningsui soon,

638
00:34:57,840 --> 00:34:58,840
and I'll give him a piece of my mind.

639
00:34:59,640 --> 00:35:01,080
Okay, talk later.

640
00:35:01,160 --> 00:35:02,000
Chairman Li,

641
00:35:02,080 --> 00:35:04,200
things aren't going smoothly with Ms. Lin.

642
00:35:04,280 --> 00:35:06,400
Could the arranged marriage
between the Lin and Li families

643
00:35:06,480 --> 00:35:07,640
be affected?

644
00:35:07,720 --> 00:35:08,920
What arranged marriage?

645
00:35:09,680 --> 00:35:12,480
This is just to offload Hailan Port
to the Lin family as quickly as possible.

646
00:35:16,800 --> 00:35:17,920
Dr. Yang.

647
00:35:20,040 --> 00:35:21,080
It's been a while.

648
00:35:25,480 --> 00:35:26,480
Mrs. Li.

649
00:35:30,720 --> 00:35:32,280
Jinyu,

650
00:35:32,360 --> 00:35:34,920
this is the budget
for Phase III of our Hailan Port project.

651
00:35:35,000 --> 00:35:35,960
Please take a look.

652
00:35:36,040 --> 00:35:37,200
If everything seems fine,

653
00:35:37,280 --> 00:35:39,000
we'll move forward

654
00:35:39,080 --> 00:35:40,400
and start by demolishing
the fishing village.

655
00:35:44,520 --> 00:35:45,600
Jinyu,

656
00:35:45,680 --> 00:35:47,400
the fishing village
is in the best location in Ningsui.

657
00:35:47,480 --> 00:35:50,320
Our Lin Group is willing
to collaborate with Hanhai Group

658
00:35:50,400 --> 00:35:51,880
on Phase III precisely

659
00:35:51,960 --> 00:35:54,000
because we recognize the strategic value
of the fishing village's location.

660
00:35:57,000 --> 00:35:58,960
How about we end here for today?

661
00:36:00,320 --> 00:36:01,840
Regarding Hailan Port Phase III,

662
00:36:01,920 --> 00:36:04,080
I need to discuss it further with my team.

663
00:36:04,160 --> 00:36:05,160
Let's talk again later.

664
00:36:08,840 --> 00:36:09,680
Alright.

665
00:36:09,760 --> 00:36:10,840
Let's go.

666
00:36:11,360 --> 00:36:12,520
I won't see you out then.

667
00:36:13,240 --> 00:36:14,240
No need to.

668
00:36:14,760 --> 00:36:16,760
- Mr. Li, no need to see us out.
- Goodbye, Jinyu.

669
00:36:23,720 --> 00:36:24,880
<i>Dad,</i>

670
00:36:25,720 --> 00:36:28,000
<i>don't forget to come home</i>
<i>for dinner tonight.</i>

671
00:36:41,280 --> 00:36:42,880
The food's here!

672
00:36:43,600 --> 00:36:44,640
Just one more soup

673
00:36:44,720 --> 00:36:45,880
and everything will be ready.

674
00:36:45,960 --> 00:36:47,400
Don't overwork yourself.
You must be exhausted.

675
00:36:47,480 --> 00:36:48,600
Not tired at all.

676
00:36:49,840 --> 00:36:51,320
I think Dad's here. I'll get the door.

677
00:36:53,560 --> 00:36:54,560
Coming!

678
00:36:55,920 --> 00:36:56,760
Dad, you're here.

679
00:36:57,600 --> 00:36:58,480
Jinyu.

680
00:36:59,320 --> 00:37:00,360
Where's Meng?

681
00:37:00,440 --> 00:37:02,240
She's waiting for you in the dining room.

682
00:37:07,720 --> 00:37:08,760
Meng.

683
00:37:26,840 --> 00:37:27,680
Dad.

684
00:37:27,760 --> 00:37:28,960
Meng

685
00:37:29,040 --> 00:37:31,160
had me prepare your favorite wine for you.

686
00:37:31,240 --> 00:37:32,840
- Please, have a taste.
- Here.

687
00:37:52,640 --> 00:37:54,600
I know you're still angry with me.

688
00:37:59,040 --> 00:38:00,080
You have to understand

689
00:38:02,120 --> 00:38:04,440
that it all happened so suddenly.

690
00:38:05,240 --> 00:38:07,120
I had no time to process it.

691
00:38:09,680 --> 00:38:11,640
At the time, I just wanted to protect you.

692
00:38:12,280 --> 00:38:13,360
Maybe…

693
00:38:14,520 --> 00:38:16,240
I was also trying
to avoid facing it myself.

694
00:38:19,560 --> 00:38:20,720
To be honest,

695
00:38:21,600 --> 00:38:22,880
your mom's sudden passing

696
00:38:22,960 --> 00:38:24,600
hit me really hard.

697
00:38:25,880 --> 00:38:27,240
I naively believed

698
00:38:28,640 --> 00:38:30,280
that as long as we never brought it up,

699
00:38:31,640 --> 00:38:33,880
the wound would never be reopened.

700
00:38:39,520 --> 00:38:41,040
Now I understand it.

701
00:38:43,520 --> 00:38:44,680
I was wrong.

702
00:38:48,760 --> 00:38:49,640
Meng,

703
00:38:51,120 --> 00:38:52,560
I apologize.

704
00:38:54,920 --> 00:38:55,880
I'm sorry.

705
00:39:02,040 --> 00:39:03,920
Actually, I can't blame you entirely.

706
00:39:05,120 --> 00:39:07,120
Even if you had told me back then,

707
00:39:07,200 --> 00:39:09,360
I probably wouldn't
have been able to handle it.

708
00:39:11,360 --> 00:39:12,920
I was too young and immature,

709
00:39:14,320 --> 00:39:15,440
prone to acting on impulse.

710
00:39:19,840 --> 00:39:21,040
So, you're not still

711
00:39:21,640 --> 00:39:23,120
angry with me now, are you?

712
00:39:25,840 --> 00:39:26,920
Let go of the past

713
00:39:28,400 --> 00:39:29,560
and live well.

714
00:39:35,160 --> 00:39:37,640
Dad, you too.

715
00:39:38,760 --> 00:39:40,640
You need to move forward.

716
00:39:40,720 --> 00:39:42,200
That's what Mom would have wanted to see.

717
00:39:45,440 --> 00:39:46,520
Alright.

718
00:39:50,360 --> 00:39:53,280
Let's toast as a family.

719
00:39:54,760 --> 00:39:55,640
Come on.

720
00:39:57,280 --> 00:39:58,720
- Come on, Dad.
- Dad.

721
00:40:05,560 --> 00:40:06,480
Jinyu.

722
00:40:09,720 --> 00:40:11,680
I am entrusting Meng to you completely.

723
00:40:12,920 --> 00:40:14,200
Thank you for your approval, Dad.

724
00:40:15,720 --> 00:40:16,800
Did you cook all these dishes yourself?

725
00:40:18,840 --> 00:40:20,040
Come on. Try his cooking.

726
00:40:20,120 --> 00:40:21,360
Let me just wash my hands first.

727
00:40:21,440 --> 00:40:22,440
Okay.

728
00:40:28,760 --> 00:40:29,640
Congratulations

729
00:40:29,720 --> 00:40:31,600
on winning over your father-in-law.

730
00:40:32,120 --> 00:40:33,200
Not bad, I guess.

731
00:40:33,720 --> 00:40:34,840
Take this off.

732
00:40:38,840 --> 00:40:40,600
You look pretty handsome in an apron.

733
00:40:40,680 --> 00:40:41,680
Really?

734
00:40:42,680 --> 00:40:44,040
Then I'll wear it more often.

735
00:40:44,120 --> 00:40:44,960
Right.

736
00:40:45,480 --> 00:40:46,600
You said it.

737
00:40:49,160 --> 00:40:50,800
No need to see me out. It's cold outside.

738
00:40:50,880 --> 00:40:51,920
Then I'll walk Dad out. You stay.

739
00:40:57,600 --> 00:40:58,560
Dad,

740
00:40:59,320 --> 00:41:01,960
actually, I wanted to talk to you

741
00:41:02,040 --> 00:41:03,520
- about something else.
- Go ahead.

742
00:41:04,440 --> 00:41:06,200
Phase III of Hailan Port

743
00:41:06,280 --> 00:41:07,760
is about to start construction.

744
00:41:09,000 --> 00:41:10,600
And the fishing village
will be demolished.

745
00:41:10,680 --> 00:41:12,200
Did you know about this?

746
00:41:12,280 --> 00:41:13,680
I know. I approved it.

747
00:41:15,040 --> 00:41:16,120
I don't understand.

748
00:41:16,720 --> 00:41:18,040
This fishing village

749
00:41:18,120 --> 00:41:20,120
is the most distinctive feature

750
00:41:20,200 --> 00:41:21,760
and cultural charm of Ningsui.

751
00:41:22,600 --> 00:41:24,920
When Hailan Port
was first established, it was promoted

752
00:41:25,000 --> 00:41:27,640
as a development based
on the existing ecosystem,

753
00:41:27,720 --> 00:41:29,560
not one that would remove it.

754
00:41:32,400 --> 00:41:33,400
You're absolutely right.

755
00:41:33,480 --> 00:41:35,360
Our little fishing village

756
00:41:35,880 --> 00:41:37,240
is indeed wonderful.

757
00:41:38,360 --> 00:41:39,520
But as you know,

758
00:41:39,600 --> 00:41:41,480
it can't be scaled up or strengthened.

759
00:41:41,560 --> 00:41:44,920
Why did the government
approve replacing our village

760
00:41:45,000 --> 00:41:46,480
with Hailan Port

761
00:41:46,560 --> 00:41:47,960
through investment promotion?

762
00:41:48,040 --> 00:41:50,360
Isn't it precisely to boost tourism here

763
00:41:50,440 --> 00:41:52,560
by bringing in big enterprises?

764
00:41:52,640 --> 00:41:55,840
But this is where Ye Meng grew up.

765
00:41:56,520 --> 00:41:59,080
It holds so many
cherished memories for everyone.

766
00:41:59,160 --> 00:42:00,080
Dad,

767
00:42:00,600 --> 00:42:02,040
how could you agree to tear it down too?

768
00:42:02,640 --> 00:42:03,840
Don't just look at me.

769
00:42:03,920 --> 00:42:05,280
See what Ye Meng said.

770
00:42:05,360 --> 00:42:07,080
We need to look forward.

771
00:42:07,160 --> 00:42:08,760
For the development of our community,

772
00:42:08,840 --> 00:42:10,400
some things must be let go.

773
00:42:10,480 --> 00:42:12,920
Alright, go spend time with Ye Meng.

774
00:42:15,040 --> 00:42:16,240
Take care on the road, Dad.

775
00:42:47,840 --> 00:42:48,880
Granny.

776
00:42:49,600 --> 00:42:50,560
Wake up.

777
00:42:50,640 --> 00:42:51,720
What's wrong?

778
00:42:51,800 --> 00:42:52,640
Granny!

779
00:42:53,280 --> 00:42:54,320
Granny!

780
00:43:01,600 --> 00:43:03,840
Look here.

781
00:43:03,920 --> 00:43:05,960
This is confirmed to be a brain tumor.

782
00:43:06,040 --> 00:43:07,760
As for whether it's malignant or not,

783
00:43:07,840 --> 00:43:09,160
we'll need to wait for a biopsy

784
00:43:09,240 --> 00:43:10,800
after surgical removal.

785
00:43:10,880 --> 00:43:13,360
The patient's condition
is very unstable right now.

786
00:43:13,440 --> 00:43:14,600
You, as the family,

787
00:43:14,680 --> 00:43:15,720
need to decide quickly

788
00:43:16,320 --> 00:43:18,520
on whether to opt for conservative
treatment or proceed with surgery.

789
00:43:19,880 --> 00:43:24,960
PLEASE SEE THE DOCTOR IN ORDER

790
00:43:33,960 --> 00:43:35,320
<i>Given your grandma's age,</i>

791
00:43:35,400 --> 00:43:37,360
<i>we actually don't recommend surgery.</i>

792
00:43:37,440 --> 00:43:38,840
<i>The risks are very high.</i>

793
00:43:39,640 --> 00:43:42,480
<i>However, if the surgery is successful,</i>
<i>she could potentially live</i>

794
00:43:42,560 --> 00:43:43,600
<i>another ten years or more.</i>

795
00:43:44,320 --> 00:43:45,400
<i>But as you know,</i>

796
00:43:45,480 --> 00:43:47,480
<i>nothing is certain.</i>

797
00:43:48,720 --> 00:43:50,320
<i>Ultimately, it's a decision</i>

798
00:43:50,400 --> 00:43:52,600
<i>that needs to be made</i>
<i>by the family after discussion.</i>

799
00:46:22,160 --> 00:46:25,840
Subtitle translation by: Wanjiao Song
